title: With Honors [Soundtrack] 320vbr
description:
By Officer Sniffy

I always collect movie soundtracks and I love this soundtrack (and also the movie). The stand out tracks for me here are "Blue Skies" Lyle Lovett, "Forever Young" The Pretenders, "She Sells Sanctuary" The Cult, "Thank You" Duran Duran, "I'll Remember" Madonna, & "Your Ghost" Kristen Hersh(and Michael Stipe) .. The only thing that I think was missing is the instrumental version of "I'll Remember" that was in the movie but either way if you love movie soundtracks, this one is a must have!
